sub_title: Executive Director - Thought Leadership and Policy at Goldman Sachs Asset Management
summary:
Sustainable finance professional focused on results. Proficient in development and execution of strategic solutions. Driven by a strong belief that finance has a purpose and should be used as a force for good. Experienced with integrating Paris Alignment objectives and climate change risk in concrete solutions for portfolio implementation across asset classes. Excellent problem solver by focusing on the crucial. Entrepreneurial, good at setting up projects, giving presentations, working together, great stakeholder management and delivering results.

Paris alignment, net zero, climate change risk, ESG, sustainability implementation, stakeholder management, commercial advisory, business strategy, project management
